  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Account Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for day-to-day operation in accounting and month-end closing to ensure timely and accurate.</li>\n  <li>Handle full set accounts (GL/AP/AR) and ensure the intercompany transactions is tally and cash flow monitoring</li>\n  <li>Assist to prepare annual budget</li>\n  <li>preparing financial statements for financial reporting as well as assisting in budgetary control, management accounting and financial analysis.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for monthly processing and submission of payroll and reports.</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely verification of timesheets and submission of payroll</li>\n  <li>CPF Submission</li>\n  <li>IR8A</li>\n  <li>PPE schedule</li>\n  <li>Tax computation &amp; Capital Allowance Schedule</li>\n  <li>Bank Reconciliations</li>\n  <li>Form C-S, ECI Filling</li>\n  <li>GST Report &amp; Submission</li>\n  <li>Liaise with external auditor</li>\n  <li>Annual Return Filling</li>\n  <li>Preparation of AGM, EGM Board Resolution &amp; etc.</li>\n  <li>Yearly closing &amp; Audit Schedule preparation</li>\n  <li>To undertake ad hoc duties as assigned from time to time</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in accountancy or higher with at least 5 years of working experience in a full set accounts position and a strong knowledge in accounting entries</li>\n  <li>Must be mature, meticulous, able to multitask and take on challenges</li>\n  <li>Team player and able to work under pressure and meet deadlines</li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skill and able to work in team/autonomously</li>\n  <li>Ability to work with all levels of management and cross functional teams</li>\n  <li>Fluent in spoken and written English.</li>\n  <li>Fluency in spoken Mandarin is a plus (in order to handle queries and converse with Mandarin in speaking external parties like)</li>\n  <li><strong>Knowledge of Quickbooks accounting system will be an added advantage.</strong></li>\n</ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 5,
